        "content": "<p>Uztaisīja velojoslas uz ielām te <a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=18/56.944133/24.079700\">https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=18/56.944133/24.079700</a> . Par  izvietojuma stulbumu tam visam man pat pateikt nav ko (pilns internets ar sūdzībām) - bet nu es neko vairāk arī negaidu Latvijā. Bet pa virsu vēl protams uzreiz sarodās idioti katrs par nākamo tizlāks: viens uz ietves stāv (zem zīmes) <img alt=\"1.jpg\" class=\"inline-image\" data-original-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-original-dimensions=\"1920x1080\" data-original-src=\"/user_uploads/49624/V3VkwquK4qLXC92jUgP4vM1t/1.jpg\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/49624/V3VkwquK4qLXC92jUgP4vM1t/1.jpg/840x560.webp\">, otrs pāri visām līnijām mauc<br>\n<img alt=\"2.jpg\" class=\"inline-image\" data-original-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-original-dimensions=\"1920x1080\" data-original-src=\"/user_uploads/49624/uQDRV72PuyhBw91crdjMORr-/2.jpg\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/49624/uQDRV72PuyhBw91crdjMORr-/2.jpg/840x560.webp\">, trešais vispār pilnībā nobloķējis velojoslu <img alt=\"3.jpg\" class=\"inline-image\" data-original-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-original-dimensions=\"1920x1080\" data-original-src=\"/user_uploads/49624/zm2Zj-P0wPunvAqapAktc5tt/3.jpg\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/49624/zm2Zj-P0wPunvAqapAktc5tt/3.jpg/840x560.webp\">. Un tas izbraucot turp šurp tikai tos 100 metrus pāris minūtes.</p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=18/56.944133/24.079700\" style='background-image: url(\"https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/6216f4773cbede236f0589ddcc1cf59e83a3b7bb/68747470733a2f2f7777772e6f70656e7374726565746d61702e6f72672f6173736574732f6f736d5f6c6f676f5f3235362d656430323866393034363832323461323732393631633338306563656530636662373362383034386233346634623462323034623766306431303937383735642e706e67\")'></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.